item.title: How do i get my server working (or online)? i have a source
item.dc:creator: @Nintendo1 Nintendo
item.description:
@Nintendo1 wrote:

Click Run Server then it must say 0:0:0:0:43594 , or 0:0:0:0:5555, or 0:0:0:0:1234 the last 4 number is your port like 0:0:0:0:43594 then 43594 is your port !

          Thanks,
            Nintendo

item.title: How do i get my server working (or online)? i have a source
item.dc:creator: @bib bib
item.description:
@bib wrote:

If your server is hamachi…
Step 1: Open your source folder and open runeserver.bat

Step 2: Open hamachi and type in the numbers on the top of the box as your server ip

Step 3: Make sure you have the correct port to login. Find out your port when you open up runserver.bat it says starting whatevrscape on 0:0:0:0:5555
